"<U+0D15><U+0D34><U+0D3F><U+0D1E><U+0D4D><U+0D1E> 45 <U+0D35><U+0D7C><U+0D37><U+0D24><U+0D4D><U+0D24><U+0D3F><U+0D28><U+0D3F><U+0D1F><U+0D2F><U+0D3F><U+0D32><U+0D46> <U+0D0F><U+0D31><U+0D4D><U+0D31><U+0D35><U+0D41><U+0D02> <U+0D09><U+0D2F><U+0D7C><U+0D28><U+0D4D><U+0D28> <U+0D28><U+0D3F><U+0D30><U+0D15><U+0D4D><U+0D15><U+0D3F><U+0D32><U+0D3E><U+0D23><U+0D4D> <U+0D24><U+0D4A><U+0D34><U+0D3F><U+0D32><U+0D3F><U+0D32><U+0D4D><U+0D32><U+0D3E><U+0D2F><U+0D4D><U+0D2E>. <U+0D08> <U+0D2A><U+0D4D><U+0D30><U+0D24><U+0D3F><U+0D38><U+0D28><U+0D4D><U+0D27><U+0D3F> <U+0D28><U+0D47><U+0D30><U+0D3F><U+0D1F><U+0D41><U+0D28><U+0D4D><U+0D28><U+0D24><U+0D3F><U+0D28><U+0D3E><U+0D2F><U+0D3F> <U+0D2A><U+0D41><U+0D24><U+0D3F><U+0D2F> <U+0D24><U+0D4A><U+0D34><U+0D3F><U+0D32><U+0D35><U+0D38><U+0D30><U+0D19><U+0D4D><U+0D19><U+0D7E> <U+0D38><U+0D43><U+0D37><U+0D4D><U+0D1F><U+0D3F><U+0D15><U+0D4D><U+0D15><U+0D41><U+0D28><U+0D4D><U+0D28><U+0D24><U+0D3F><U+0D28><U+0D4D><U+0D31><U+0D46> <U+0D05><U+0D1F><U+0D3F><U+0D38><U+0D4D><U+0D25><U+0D3E><U+0D28><U+0D24><U+0D4D><U+0D24><U+0D3F><U+0D7D> <U+0D15><U+0D2E><U+0D4D><U+0D2A><U+0D28><U+0D3F><U+0D15><U+0D7E><U+0D15><U+0D4D><U+0D15><U+0D4D> <U+0D2A><U+0D4D><U+0D30><U+0D24><U+0D4D><U+0D2F><U+0D47><U+0D15> <U+0D06><U+0D28><U+0D41><U+0D15><U+0D42><U+0D32><U+0D4D><U+0D2F><U+0D19><U+0D4D><U+0D19><U+0D33><U+0D41><U+0D02> <U+0D28><U+0D3F><U+0D15><U+0D41><U+0D24><U+0D3F> <U+0D07><U+0D33><U+0D35><U+0D41><U+0D15><U+0D33><U+0D41><U+0D02> <U+0D28><U+0D7D><U+0D15><U+0D41><U+0D02>."
"We will make it easier to do business by radically simplifying GST with a single, low tax rate &amp; basic tax structure."
"We vow to protect Indias forests, wildlife, rivers and other natural resources, and work towards mitigating the effects of climate change."
"Your Freedom is your Right. We promise to uphold your rights &amp; ensure you have the freedom to be the person YOU choose."
"To compete with global manufacturing giants, we promise to promote local businesses &amp; provide them with the platform to manufacture for the world."
"We promise to remove Angel tax as we believe it contadict the philosophy of start-ups. We believe in our entrepreneurs &amp; we will support them."
"We promise to restore the autonomy our institutions such as the RBI, ECI, CBI, CIC without fear or favour."
"Under our comprehensive jobs plan, we will provide 34 lakh government &amp; public sector jobs."
"We promise the Right to Healthcare Act, guaranteeing every citizen free diagnostics &amp; medicines in our network of public hospitals."
"We promise to work with experts to resolve Indias pollution crisis and fight for our Citizens right to cleaner air, water and land."
"Our paramilitary forces sacrifice their lives on a daily basis but do not have access to adequate infrastructure. We promise to give Shaheed status to our Paramilitary forces."
"To ensure every student has access to higher education we will increase the number of scholarships provided &amp; ensure interest-free loans to students."
"We will forbid the misuse of Aadhaar and restore its usage to its original purpose according to the Aadhaar Act."
"Double the allocation for education to 6% of GDP."
"We promise to prioritise citizens privacy and bring a new law to protect it at all costs."
"We will raise the national education budget to 6% of GDP, so that every child acquires complete &amp; free quality education up to class 12."
"Aadhaar for empowerment, not exclusion or exploitation."
"We will never achieve our developmental capabilities without our women in the workforce. We promise to reserve 33% of central govt. jobs only for women."
"Price rise has greatly affected the average Indian, in order to ensure fuel prices are stabilised, we will bring Petrol &amp; Diesel under GST."
"We will raise the national education budget to 6% of GDP, so that every child acquires complete &amp; free quality education up to class 12."
"We promise to free MSMEs from the clutches of inspector raj by exempting them from all government permissions for the first three years."
"We will ensure our cities are empowered through directly elected Mayors, to ensure accountability"
"We will reverse the trend of declining defence expenditure by raising it to 3% of GDP. We will rapidly modern defence technology &amp; increase manufacturing in India."
"Through the Nyuntam Aay Yojana we will guarantee a minimum yearly income of Rs. 72,000 to 5 crore poorest families, which will be transferred directly to the woman&#039;s account."
"We promise to bring back Special Status to North Eastern States &amp; ensure they receive assistance from the central govt."
"We are committed to protecting the indigenous culture of North Eatsern states &amp; will thereby ensure the Citizenship Amendment Bill is not passed."
"We promise to ensure zero tolerance to violence of all forms and prevent hate crimes, through a comprehensive law to end such violent acts."
"We vow to protect Indias forests, wildlife, rivers and other natural resources, and work towards mitigating the effects of climate change."
"&quot;The women of India will get their due and we promise to pass Womens Reservation Bill in the first parliamentary session. <br /> &quot;"
"We promise to work with experts to resolve Indias pollution crisis and fight for our Citizens right to cleaner air, water and land."
"Our paramilitary forces sacrifice their lives on a daily basis but do not have access to adequate infrastructure. We promise to give Shaheed status to our Paramilitary forces."
"Your Freedom is your Right. We promise to uphold your rights &amp; ensure you have the freedom to be the person YOU choose."
"We promise the Right to Healthcare Act, guaranteeing every citizen free diagnostics &amp; medicines in our network of public hospitals."
"Price rise has greatly affected the average Indian, in order to ensure fuel prices are stabilised, we will bring Petrol &amp; Diesel under GST."
"We promise to prioritise citizens privacy and bring a new law to protect it at all costs."
"Under our comprehensive jobs plan, we will provide 34 lakh government &amp; public sector jobs."
"We will reverse the trend of declining defence expenditure by raising it to 3% of GDP. We will rapidly modern defence technology &amp; increase manufacturing in India."
"Double the allocation for education to 6% of GDP."
"We promise to restore the autonomy our institutions such as the RBI, ECI, CBI, CIC without fear or favour."
"Aadhaar for empowerment, not exclusion or exploitation."
"We will raise the national education budget to 6% of GDP, so that every child acquires complete &amp; free quality education up to class 12."
"We promise to bring back Special Status to North Eastern States &amp; ensure they receive assistance from the central govt."
"We promise to ensure zero tolerance to violence of all forms and prevent hate crimes, through a comprehensive law to end such violent acts."
